Title: Winged Migration
Director: Jacques Perrin, Jacques Cluzaud(co-director), Michel Debats(co-director)
Writer: Jean Dorst (collaboration), Stéphane Durand, Guy Jarry (collaboration), Valentine Marvel (idea), Jacques Perrin, Francis Roux (collaboration)
Plot: Documentary on the migratory patterns of birds, shot over the course of three years on all seven continents.
Awards: Nominated for 1 Oscar. Another 5 wins & 14 nominations.
